data.title: True Thompson
data.meta_description: True Thompson (born April 12, 2018) is Khloé & Tristan's daughter and Tatum's older sister. True is also Prince's younger half-sister and is Theo’s older half-sister. True was named after her great-great grandpa, True Otis Houghton & her great-grandpa, Robert True Houghton. True's...
